TITLE: Implementing Device Actor with Read and Write Protocols in C#
DESCRIPTION: Full implementation of a Device actor in Akka.NET, handling both temperature queries and temperature recording. Includes message handling for ReadTemperature, RecordTemperature, and corresponding response messages.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akkadotnet/akka.net/blob/dev/docs/articles/intro/getting-started/tutorial-2.md#2025-04-16_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
public sealed class Device : UntypedActor
{
    private double? _temperature;

    protected override void OnReceive(object message)
    {
        switch (message)
        {
            case RecordTemperature recordTemperature:
                _temperature = recordTemperature.Value;
                Sender.Tell(new TemperatureRecorded(recordTemperature.Id));
                break;
            case ReadTemperature readTemperature:
                Sender.Tell(new RespondTemperature(readTemperature.RequestId, _temperature));
                break;
        }
    }
}
```

