TITLE: Implementing Producer Controller with Message Chunking in Akka.Delivery
DESCRIPTION: Code example showing how to register a Producer with a ProducerController that has message chunking enabled. ChunkLargeMessagesBytes is set to create 100KB chunks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akkadotnet/akka.net/blob/dev/docs/articles/actors/reliable-delivery.md#2025-04-16_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
private ActorSystem system = ActorSystem.Create("test");
private IActorRef producerController;

private void CreateProducerWithController()
{
    var producerId = "p1";
    var settings = ProducerController.Settings.Create(system)
        .WithChunkLargeMessagesBytes(100 * 1024); // 100KB chunks
    producerController = system.ActorOf(ProducerController.Props(producerId, settings));
    // create producer
    var producer = system.ActorOf(Props.Create(() => new Producer(producerController)));
    // register producer with the controller
    producerController.Tell(new ProducerController.Start<string>(producer));
}
```

