TITLE: Implementing Confirmable Messages with AskNextTo in Akka.Delivery
DESCRIPTION: Code showing how to use the AskNextTo method to get confirmation when messages are persisted. The producer receives the sequence number after the message has been stored in the EventSourcedProducerQueue.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akkadotnet/akka.net/blob/dev/docs/articles/actors/reliable-delivery.md#2025-04-16_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
class Producer : ReceiveActor
{
    private IActorRef _controller;
    private long _nextSequenceNr = 0;

    public Producer(IActorRef controller)
    {
        _controller = controller;

        Receive<string>(message => {
            var nextMsg = new ProducerController.RequestNext<string>(
                AskNextTo: Self,
                MessageMapper: _ => message);

            _controller.Tell(nextMsg);
        });

        Receive<ProducerController.MessageWithConfirmation<string>>(confirmed => {
            _nextSequenceNr = confirmed.SequenceNr;
            // message with sequence number confirmed.SequenceNr has been persisted
        });
    }
}
```

