TITLE: Implementing Entity Termination Logic in C#
DESCRIPTION: Example of how to properly terminate remembered entities using passivation in an Akka.NET actor implementation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akkadotnet/akka.net/blob/dev/docs/articles/clustering/cluster-sharding.md#2025-04-16_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
protected override bool ReceiveCommand(object message)
{
    switch (message)
    {
        case Increment _:
            Persist(new CounterChanged(1), UpdateState);
            return true;
        case Decrement _:
            Persist(new CounterChanged(-1), UpdateState);
            return true;
        case Get _:
            Sender.Tell(_count);
            return true;
        case ReceiveTimeout _:
            Context.Parent.Tell(new Passivate(Stop.Instance));
            return true;
        case Stop _:
            Context.Stop(Self);
            return true;
    }
    return false;
}
```

