TITLE: Pattern Matching on Member Object in C# 8
DESCRIPTION: This C# 8 code demonstrates pattern matching using a switch expression. It checks if the input 'member' is a `Member` object and returns the result of `HasRole`. If not, returns `true`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akkadotnet/akka.net/blob/dev/docs/community/contributing/porting-guide.md#2025-04-16_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: c#
CODE:
```
public bool MatchingRole(Member member, string role)
    => member switch 
    {
        Member m => m.HasRole(role),
        _ => true
    }
```

