TITLE: Implementing ReadHighestSequenceNrAsync Method for Akka.Persistence Journal
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of the ReadHighestSequenceNrAsync method for a SQLite-based Akka.Persistence journal. This method retrieves the highest stored sequence number for a given persistence ID.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akkadotnet/akka.net/blob/dev/docs/articles/persistence/custom-persistence-provider.md#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
protected override async Task<long> ReadHighestSequenceNrAsync(string persistenceId, long fromSequenceNr)
{
    using (var connection = await _connectionFactory.CreateConnection())
    using (var command = connection.CreateCommand())
    {
        command.CommandText = HighestSequenceNrSql;
        command.Parameters.AddWithValue("@PersistenceId", persistenceId);

        var result = await command.ExecuteScalarAsync();
        return result == DBNull.Value ? 0L : Convert.ToInt64(result);
    }
}
