TITLE: Implementing Message Production in Producer Actor for Akka.Cluster.Sharding.Delivery in C#
DESCRIPTION: Shows how a Producer actor handles RequestNext messages from the ShardingProducerController and sends messages wrapped in ShardingEnvelope.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akkadotnet/akka.net/blob/dev/docs/articles/clustering/cluster-sharding-delivery.md#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
private void OnRequestNext(ShardingProducerController.RequestNext<IConfirmableMessage> next)
{
    var messages = GenerateMessages();
    foreach (var msg in messages)
    {
        var entityId = ExtractEntityId(msg);
        _producerController.Tell(
            new ShardingEnvelope(entityId, msg));
    }
    Sender.Tell(ShardingProducerController.ConsumeNextCredit<IConfirmableMessage>.Instance);
}
```

