TITLE: Configuring Static Quorum Strategy in Akka.NET
DESCRIPTION: Configuration for the static-quorum strategy which downs unreachable nodes if the number of reachable ones meets the quorum size. This strategy works well when you can define a minimum required cluster size.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akkadotnet/akka.net/blob/dev/docs/articles/clustering/split-brain-resolver.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: hocon
CODE:
```
akka.cluster.split-brain-resolver {
  active-strategy = static-quorum

  static-quorum {
    # minimum number of nodes that the cluster must have 
    quorum-size = undefined

    # if the 'role' is defined the decision is based only on members with that 'role'
    role = ""
  }
}
```

