TITLE: Testing Array Substitution in HOCON Configuration with C#
DESCRIPTION: This test demonstrates array substitution in HOCON configuration by defining arrays in the configuration and substituting them into other properties. It verifies that arrays are correctly substituted and merged according to HOCON rules.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akkadotnet/akka.net/blob/dev/docs/articles/configuration/hocon.md#2025-04-16_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
[Fact]
public void ArraySubstitutionTest()
{
    var hocon = @"{
            arrays {
                a: [1, 2, 3]
                b: ${arrays.a}
                c: ${arrays.b}[4]
            }
        }";

    var config = ConfigurationFactory.ParseString(hocon);

    Assert.Equal(new[] { 1, 2, 3 }, config.GetIntList("arrays.a"));
    Assert.Equal(new[] { 1, 2, 3 }, config.GetIntList("arrays.b"));
    Assert.Equal(new[] { 1, 2, 3, 4 }, config.GetIntList("arrays.c"));
}
```

